---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us - AI Square"
  description="Learn about AI Square's mission to empower businesses with cutting-edge AI solutions. Discover our story, values, and the team behind the innovation."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 border-b border-border">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight">
          About <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">AI Square</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-muted-foreground">
          We're on a mission to democratize AI technology and make it accessible to businesses of all sizes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              At AI Square, we believe that artificial intelligence should be a tool for empowerment, not complexity. Our mission is to create AI solutions that are powerful yet accessible, innovative yet practical.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              We're dedicated to helping businesses harness the power of AI to solve real-world problems, improve efficiency, and unlock new opportunities for growth.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-purple-600/20 p-12 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center space-y-4">
              <div class="text-6xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">9+</div>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold">AI Products</p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Transforming businesses worldwide</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-muted/30">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Our Values</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
            The principles that guide everything we do
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="space-y-4 p-6 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Innovation First</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              We constantly push the boundaries of what's possible with AI, staying at the forefront of technological advancement.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 p-6 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Customer Centric</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              Our customers' success is our success. We build solutions that address real business needs and deliver measurable value.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 p-6 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Ethical AI</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              We're committed to developing AI responsibly, with transparency, fairness, and respect for privacy at the core.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Our Story</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert mx-auto">
          <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
            AI Square was founded with a simple vision: to bridge the gap between cutting-edge AI technology and practical business applications. We recognized that while AI had immense potential, many businesses struggled to harness its power effectively.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
            Our journey began with a small team of AI researchers and engineers who were passionate about making AI accessible. We started by developing our first product, an AI chat assistant, and quickly realized there was a massive demand for well-designed, practical AI solutions.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
            Today, we're proud to offer a comprehensive suite of AI products that serve businesses across various industries. From recruitment automation to voice agents, from document analysis to content generation, our products are helping companies work smarter and achieve more.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
            As we continue to grow, our commitment remains unchanged: to develop AI solutions that are powerful, accessible, and truly valuable to the businesses that use them.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 via-purple-500/5 to-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
          Ready to Get Started?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Discover how AI Square's products can transform your business operations.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
          <a
            href="/products"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 px-8"
          >
            Explore Products
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none border border-input bg-background hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-11 px-8"
          >
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
